'''圣亚拿圣三一堂'''（St. Ann's and the Holy Trinity Church）是一座古老的[[圣公会|圣公会]]教堂，位于[[纽约市|纽约市]][[布鲁克林区|布鲁克林区]][[布鲁克林高地|布鲁克林高地]]蒙塔古街与克林顿街转角。

==历史==
[[File:Holy_Trinity_church_windows.jpg|thumb]]
该建筑原为圣三一堂，建于1847年。1957年关闭，空置12年之久。1969年，布鲁克林最古老的圣公会堂区圣亚拿堂（1787年建立）迁入当时空置的圣三一堂。该堂拥有美国一些最古老的花窗玻璃。该堂于1987年列为[[美國國家歷史地標|美國國家歷史地標]]<ref name="nhlsum"/><ref name="nrhpinv">{{cite web |url=http://pdfhost.focus.nps.gov/docs/NHLS/Text/87002590.pdf |date=1983 |first=Carolyn |last=Pitts |others=Illust. Minard LaFever |title=National Register of Historic Places Inventory-Nomination: Holy Trinity (Protestant Episcopal) Church |format=pdf |website=National Park Service |access-date=2015-07-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120208092209/http://pdfhost.focus.nps.gov/docs/NHLS/Text/87002590.pdf |archive-date=2012-02-08 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="nrhpphotos">{{cite web |url=http://pdfhost.focus.nps.gov/docs/NHLS/Photos/87002590.pdf |title=National Register of Historic Places Inventory-Nomination: Holy Trinity (Protestant Episcopal) Church—Accompanying photos |format=pdf |date=1983 |website=National Park Service |access-date=2015-07-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120208092101/http://pdfhost.focus.nps.gov/docs/NHLS/Photos/87002590.pdf |archive-date=2012-02-08 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

圣三一堂的设计者是19世纪美国杰出建筑师Minard Lafever，花窗玻璃出自威廉·博尔顿之手<ref>{{cite news | url=http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9502E0DD173EF93BA3575AC0A9649C8B63 | work=The New York Times | title=Streetscapes/Packer Collegiate Institute; A Touch of Ivy League Grows in Brooklyn Heights | first=Christopher | last=Gray | date=September 8, 2002 | accessdate=2015-07-27 | archive-date=2007-08-17 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070817194716/http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9502E0DD173EF93BA3575AC0A9649C8B63 | dead-url=no }}</ref> 。

